This repo contains Yvan Richard's R package, and customisation files for R, emacs, screen, bash, and vim.

make 	  	: convert functions in myfunctions.r into package yrpkg, and install package
make r		: copy .Rprofile in customisation folder to ~
make y		: copy all customisation files to ~
make updatepkg  : copy customisation files from ~ to ./customisations